    <title>Incentives, Framing, and Reliance on Algorithmic Advice: An Experimental Study</title>
    <updated>2025-05-30T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Ben Greiner, Philipp Grünwald, Thomas Lindner, Georg Lintner, Martin Wiernsperger</name>
